## Project Purpose

- This is a modern React component library.
- It combines the best patterns, accessibility, and developer experience from leading libraries such as shadcn/ui, HeorUI, and Ant Design.
- The goal is to provide a cohesive, flexible, and highly customizable set of components for rapid application development.
- Emphasis on accessibility, composability, and design consistency.
